org.whispersystems.libsignal.groups.state

Class SenderKeyState

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.whispersystems.libsignal.groups.state.SenderKeyState

  • public class SenderKeyState
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents the state of an individual SenderKey ratchet. An established Group Session encapsulate the SenderKey state. SenderKeyState is maintained in durable records.
